DllEntryPoint = idb.analysis.Functions(kernel32_idb).functions[1754273429]
struc = idb.analysis.Struct(kernel32_idb, DllEntryPoint.frame)
members = list(struc.get_members())
assert list(map(lambda m: m.get_name(), members)) == [' s', ' r',
    'hinstDLL', 'fdwReason', 'lpReserved']
assert members[2].get_type() == 'HINSTANCE'
kern32_test([(695, 32, None), (695, 64, None), (700, 32, None), (700, 64,
    None)])
